    <div class="info-box">
        <h2>Jio Overview</h2>
        <p>Jio, also known as Reliance Jio, is a telecommunications company in India. It is a subsidiary of Reliance Industries Limited, and it was launched in September 2016.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="info-box">
        <h2>Jio Services</h2>
        <p>Jio offers a wide range of services, including 4G data services, high-speed internet, digital television, and various digital services. Jio is known for its affordable data plans and extensive network coverage.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="info-box">
        <h2>Jio 4G Network</h2>
        <p>Jio is widely recognized for its 4G network, which has played a significant role in the digital transformation of India. The company has gained a large customer base due to its competitive pricing and innovative offerings.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="info-box">
        <h2>JioFiber</h2>
        <p>JioFiber is Jio's fiber-to-the-home broadband service, offering high-speed internet, television services, and home automation. It provides users with a seamless and high-quality internet experience.</p>
    </div>

